Step 1
●. Design Fundamentals

Design pincipals.

- Color & Contrast (UI design)
	> Using right contrast color.

- White space
	padding, margin etc.

- Visual Hierarchy
	Emphasies characters

- Complexity vs Simplicity

- Consistency
	same patterns, same designs..

Step 2
●. Designing & Prototyping UI's
	Creating markup, prototypes for prepare other requests.

●. Choose your weapon of choice.
	- Old-schoolded way
	- New-schoolded way

	Sketch - photoshop, W-xd, Pigma, invision-app, gravity, framer, principle etc.

	Sketch, W-xd, Pigma

Step 3
●. HTML & CSS

	- Code Editors
		Visual Studio Code, SublimeText

	- Understanding HTML
	- Understanding CSS
	- Undersainding Sass
		# Syntactically Awesome Style Sheets.
		# A preprocessor that enhances the power of CSS.
			Allow you to write css for instance with differenct features.
			Will output regular css for you.

